    <sectiondef kind="user-defined">
      <header>ESP32 pin configuration bit field layout</header>
      <description><para>ESP32 pin configuration bit field.</para>
<para>This field encodes pin configuration options used by the ESP32 pinctrl driver.</para>
<para>Fields:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>bias [ 0 : 1 ]</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>drive [ 2 : 3 ]</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>output level [ 4 : 5 ]</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>input/output enable override [ 6 : 7 ]</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>sleep hold [ 8 ]</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>These values are combined into a single integer and later translated into GPIO configuration flags by the driver. </para>
</description>
